  "implementationNotes": [
    "Do not treat elements as isolated presets.",
    "When multiple elements are near the same target, calculate dominant, modifiers and residue.",
    "Sub-emotions inherit family tendencies but need individual deviations.",
    "Image modulation should include material interference, not just color overlays.",
    "Sound modulation should include envelope, texture and time behavior, not just pitch/filter/volume."
  ]
